   property in the plugin's configuration object to
   <code>
    content14
   </code>
   .
   <br/>
   <br/>
   See
   <a href="#examples">
    content15
   </a>
   for more details.
  </p>
  <p>
   You can change the selection area of copy/paste range by setting
