    content16
   </code>
   property to
   <code>
    content17
   </code>
   or
   <code>
    content18
   </code>
   .
      By default this property is set to
   <code>
    content19
   </code>
   . If set to
   <code>
    content20
   </code>
   , then hidden columns are being skipped for copy/paste actions.
